<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>第五人格 · 充值场景客服分析报告</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/echarts@5/dist/echarts.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
      background: #0f1117;
      color: #e0e6f0;
      display: flex;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ===== 左侧导航 ===== */
    .sidebar {
      width: 220px;
      min-width: 220px;
      background: #161b27;
      border-right: 1px solid #252d40;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .sidebar-logo {
      padding: 24px 20px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #252d40;
    }

    .sidebar-logo .game-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #5a6a8a;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .sidebar-logo .title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #c8d8f8;
    }

    .sidebar-logo .subtitle {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #4a5a7a;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .nav-group-label {
      padding: 16px 20px 6px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #3a4a6a;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 11px 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6a7a9a;
      border-left: 3px solid transparent;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-item:hover {
      background: #1e2535;
      color: #a0b4d8;
    }

    .nav-item.active {
      background: #1a2540;
      color: #6aa3ff;
      border-left: 3px solid #6aa3ff;
    }

    .nav-item .icon { font-size: 15px; width: 20px; text-align: center; }

    .sidebar-footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #252d40;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3a4a6a;
    }

    /* ===== 主内容区 ===== */
    .main {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 28px 32px;
    }

    .page { display: none; }
    .page.active { display: block; }

    /* ===== 通用标题 ===== */
    .page-header {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #252d40;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #d0e0ff;
    }

    .page-header p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4a5a7a;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    /* ===== 数据卡片 ===== */
    .kpi-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .kpi-card {
      background: #161b27;
      border: 1px solid #252d40;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .kpi-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
    }

    .kpi-card.blue::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3a7bd5, #6aa3ff); }
    .kpi-card.green::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #27ae60, #2ecc71); }
    .kpi-card.orange::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e67e22, #f39c12); }
    .kpi-card.purple::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8e44ad, #9b59b6); }
    .kpi-card.red::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c0392b, #e74c3c); }
    .kpi-card.teal::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #16a085, #1abc9c); }

    .kpi-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #5a6a8a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .kpi-value {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #d0e0ff;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .kpi-value span {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #6a7a9a;
      margin-left: 2px;
    }

    .kpi-note {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3a4a6a;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* ===== 图表容器 ===== */
    .chart-row {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .chart-row.col2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .chart-row.col3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }

    .chart-card {
      background: #161b27;
      border: 1px solid #252d40;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .chart-card h3 {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #8a9ab8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .chart-box { width: 100%; height: 240px; }

    /* ===== 注释块 ===== */
    .note-block {
      background: #1a2035;
      border: 1px solid #2a3a5a;
      border-left: 3px solid #4a7adf;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7a9ac8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .note-block.warn {
      border-left-color: #e67e22;
      background: #1e1a10;
      color: #c8a060;
    }

    /* ===== 表格 ===== */
    .data-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .data-table th {
      background: #1e2535;
      color: #6a8ab8;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #252d40;
    }

    .data-table td {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2535;
      color: #a0b0cc;
    }

    .data-table tr:hover td { background: #1a2030; }

    .data-table .highlight { color: #6aa3ff; font-weight: 600; }
    .data-table .warn-text { color: #e67e22; }
    .data-table .good-text { color: #2ecc71; }

    /* ===== 优先级徽章 ===== */
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .badge.p0 { background: #3d1212; color: #e74c3c; border: 1px solid #5a1a1a; }
    .badge.p1 { background: #3d2a10; color: #f39c12; border: 1px solid #5a3a15; }
    .badge.p2 { background: #1a2d1a; color: #2ecc71; border: 1px solid #1e3d1e; }

    /* ===== 场景卡片 ===== */
    .scene-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .scene-card {
      background: #161b27;
      border: 1px solid #252d40;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .scene-card:hover { border-color: #3a5a9a; }

    .scene-card.selected { border-color: #6aa3ff; background: #1a2540; }

    .scene-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #c0d0f0;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .scene-count {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #6aa3ff;
    }

    .scene-count span { font-size: 12px; color: #5a6a8a; margin-left: 2px; }

    .scene-pct {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #5a6a8a;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .progress-bar-wrap {
      height: 4px;
      background: #252d40;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3a6ad5, #6aa3ff);
    }

    /* ===== 问题列表 ===== */
    .issue-list { margin-bottom: 20px; }

    .issue-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2535;
    }

    .issue-rank {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #252d40;
      color: #6a7a9a;
      font-size: 11px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .issue-rank.top { background: #2a3a6a; color: #6aa3ff; }

    .issue-name { flex: 1; font-size: 12px; color: #a0b0cc; }

    .issue-bar-wrap {
      width: 100px;
      height: 4px;
      background: #252d40;
      border-radius: 2px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .issue-bar {
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3a6ad5, #6aa3ff);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .issue-pct { font-size: 12px; color: #6aa3ff; width: 38px; text-align: right; }

    /* ===== 优化建议卡片 ===== */
    .suggest-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .suggest-card {
      background: #161b27;
      border: 1px solid #252d40;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .suggest-card h3 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #c0d0f0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .suggest-card ul {
      padding-left: 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7a8aaa;
      line-height: 2;
    }

    .suggest-card .owner {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3a4a6a;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding-top: 8px;
      border-top: 1px solid #252d40;
    }

    /* ===== 分隔 ===== */
    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3a4a6a;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    /* ===== 滚动条 ===== */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #252d40; border-radius: 3px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== 左侧导航 ===== -->
<aside class="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-logo">
    <div class="game-tag">Identity V · h55</div>
    <div class="title">充值场景客服分析</div>
    <div class="subtitle">数据周期：2025年3月</div>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-group-label">报告模块</div>

  <div class="nav-item active" onclick="switchPage('overview', this)">
    <span class="icon">📊</span> 整体概览
  </div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPage('scene', this)">
    <span class="icon">📦</span> 场景分析
  </div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPage('core', this)">
    <span class="icon">⚠️</span> 核心问题
  </div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPage('ticket', this)">
    <span class="icon">📋</span> 工单专项
  </div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPage('suggest', this)">
    <span class="icon">✅</span> 优化建议
  </div>

  <div class="sidebar-footer">
    数据截止 2025.03.29<br/>
    清洗范围 02.23–03.23
  </div>
</aside>

<!-- ===== 主内容区 ===== -->
<main class="main">

  <!-- ========== 页面1：整体概览 ========== -->
  <section class="page active" id="page-overview">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>整体概览</h1>
      <p>3月服务数据（截止29号）· 第五人格 h55 · 全场景</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">核心 KPI</div>
    <div class="kpi-grid">
      <div class="kpi-card blue">
        <div class="kpi-label">总服务量</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">406,255<span>条</span></div>
        <div class="kpi-note">3月全渠道累计</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi-card green">
        <div class="kpi-label">智能解决占比</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">75.00<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="kpi-note">约 304,691 条智能解决</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi-card orange">
        <div class="kpi-label">人工服务量</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">41,426<span>条</span></div>
        <div class="kpi-note">人工服务占比 10.20%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi-card purple">
        <div class="kpi-label">整体 FCR</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">81.68<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="kpi-note">人工 FCR 79.39%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi-card teal">
        <div class="kpi-label">好评率</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">78.79<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="kpi-note">满意度评价</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi-card red">
        <div class="kpi-label">提单比 / 转单率</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">14.59<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="kpi-note">人工无法一次解决转工单</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chart-row col2">
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>服务量构成</h3>
        <div class="chart-box" id="chart-service-pie"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>关键指标一览</h3>
        <div class="chart-box" id="chart-kpi-bar"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="note-block">
      💡 <strong>数据说明</strong>：3月整体服务量超40万，智能解决占比达75%，人工服务占比仅10.20%，但仍有约41,426条进入人工；转单率14.59%，说明人工仍有相当比例无法一次性解决，需进一步提单处理。
    </div>

    <div class="section-label" style="margin-top:4px;">本次分析数据说明</div>
    <div class="chart-card">
      <h3>充值场景专项数据范围（清洗数据）</h3>
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>项目</th>
            <th>说明</th>
            <th>备注</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>数据时间范围</td>
            <td class="highlight">2月23日 — 3月23日</td>
            <td>约一个月跨度，含2月末活动期</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>充值场景人工对话总量</td>
            <td class="highlight">66,231 条</td>
            <td>清洗前全量，含噪声数据</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>清洗后有效分析样本</td>
            <td class="highlight">4,293 条</td>
            <td>充值问题有效样本</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>全场景工单总量（同期）</td>
            <td class="highlight">4,066 条</td>
            <td>全场景工单</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== 页面2：场景分析 ========== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-scene">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>场景分析</h1>
      <p>基于清洗后 4,293 条有效样本 · 六大充值场景分布与 TOP 问题</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">场景分布（点击查看详细问题）</div>
    <div class="scene-grid" id="scene-grid">
      <!-- JS 渲染 -->
    </div>

    <div class="chart-row col2">
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>六大场景占比</h3>
        <div class="chart-box" id="chart-scene-pie"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>场景问题量对比</h3>
        <div class="chart-box" id="chart-scene-bar"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label" id="detail-label">场景 TOP 问题详情</div>
    <div class="chart-card" id="scene-detail-card">
      <h3 id="detail-title">点击上方场景卡片查看详情</h3>
      <div id="detail-content" style="color:#5a6a8a;font-size:12px;padding:8px 0;">请选择一个场景</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== 页面3：核心问题 ========== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-core">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>核心问题专项分析</h1>
      <p>贯穿多场景的结构性问题，影响大、需优先关注</p>
    </div>

    <div class="note-block warn">
      ⚠️ <strong>关于优惠券问题说明</strong>：本次清洗数据（2月23日—3月23日）期间，2月上线了7折卡限时活动，导致优惠券相关问题在各场景中占比异常偏高。由于该活动属一次性运营行为，后续不再复刻，预计问题量将显著回落，<strong>本次不列为高优先级优化项</strong>，建议制定活动上线标准预案。
    </div>

    <!-- P0 问题 -->
    <div class="section-label">🔴 P0 优先级问题</div>
    <div class="chart-row col2">
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>① 账号风控 / 无法充值</h3>
        <div class="issue-list">
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank top">1</div>
            <div class="issue-name">风控触发 · 账号被限制充值</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:100%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~37%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank top">2</div>
            <div class="issue-name">申诉流程不清晰 · 用户无从下手</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:65%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~24%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank">3</div>
            <div class="issue-name">充值页面卡死 / 加载异常</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:54%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~20%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank">4</div>
            <div class="issue-name">渠道服充值异常</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:35%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~13%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="note-block" style="margin-bottom:0;font-size:11px;">
          用户体验损伤大，风控申诉链路长，人工处理成本高，需优化申诉引导话术及自助流程。
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>② 货币 / 回声真实未到账</h3>
        <div class="issue-list">
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank top">1</div>
            <div class="issue-name">充值成功但游戏内货币未到账</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:100%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~28%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank top">2</div>
            <div class="issue-name">回声真实发放延迟 / 未发放</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:75%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~21%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank">3</div>
            <div class="issue-name">充值不计入氪条 / 累充活动</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:39%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~11%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank">4</div>
            <div class="issue-name">核查流程繁琐 · 用户催单多</div>
            <div class="issue-bar-wrap"><div class="issue-bar" style="width:30%"></div></div>
            <div class="issue-pct">~8%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="note-block" style="margin-bottom:0;font-size:11px;">
          直接影响用户资损感知，投诉风险高；核查链路可通过话术标准化 + 自助查单工具降低人工处理量。
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- P1 问题 -->
    <div class="section-label" style="margin-top:8px;">🟡 P1 优先级问题</div>
    <div class="chart-row col2">
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>③ 充值记录入口不清晰</h3>
        <div class="issue-list">
          <div class="issue-item">
            <div class="issue-rank top">1</div>
